        "latin_17": "laqad kafarallażīna qālū innallāha huwal-masīḥubnu maryam, qul fa may yamliku minallāhi syai`an in arāda ay yuhlikal-masīḥabna maryama wa ummahụ wa man fil-arḍi jamī'ā, wa lillāhi mulkus-samāwāti wal-arḍi wa mā bainahumā, yakhluqu mā yasyā`, wallāhu 'alā kulli syai`ing qadīr",
