        "latin_72": "fa anjaināhu wallażīna ma'ahụ biraḥmatim minnā wa qaṭa'nā dābirallażīna każżabụ bi`āyātinā wa mā kānụ mu`minīn",
        "latin_73": "wa ilā ṡamụda akhāhum ṣāliḥā, qāla yā qaumi'budullāha mā lakum min ilāhin gairuh, qad jā`atkum bayyinatum mir rabbikum, hāżihī nāqatullāhi lakum āyatan fa żarụhā ta`kul fī arḍillāhi wa lā tamassụhā bisū`in fa ya`khużakum 'ażābun alīm",
