        "latin_75": "qālal-mala`ullażīnastakbarụ ming qaumihī lillażīnastuḍ'ifụ liman āmana min-hum a ta'lamụna anna ṣāliḥam mursalum mir rabbih, qālū innā bimā ursila bihī mu`minụn",
