        "latin_95": "ṡumma baddalnā makānas-sayyi`atil-ḥasanata ḥattā 'afaw wa qālụ qad massa ābā`anaḍ-ḍarrā`u was-sarrā`u fa akhażnāhum bagtataw wa hum lā yasy'urụn",
        "latin_96": "walau anna ahlal-qurā āmanụ wattaqau lafataḥnā 'alaihim barakātim minas-samā`i wal-arḍi wa lāking każżabụ fa akhażnāhum bimā kānụ yaksibụn",
