        "latin_64": "wa ataināka bil-ḥaqqi wa innā laṣādiqụn",
        "latin_65": "fa asri bi`ahlika biqiṭ'im minal-laili wattabi' adbārahum wa lā yaltafit mingkum aḥaduw wamḍụ ḥaiṡu tu`marụn",
        "latin_66": "wa qaḍainā ilaihi żālikal-amra anna dābira hā`ulā`i maqṭụ'um muṣbiḥīn",
        "latin_67": "wa jā`a ahlul-madīnati yastabsyirụn",
        "latin_68": "qāla inna hā`ulā`i ḍaifī fa lā tafḍaḥụn",
        "latin_69": "wattaqullāha wa lā tukhzụn",
