        "latin_72": "la'amruka innahum lafī sakratihim ya'mahụn",
        "latin_73": "fa akhażat-humuṣ-ṣaiḥatu musyriqīn",
        "latin_74": "fa ja'alnā 'āliyahā sāfilahā wa amṭarnā 'alaihim ḥijāratam min sijjīl",
        "latin_75": "inna fī żālika la`āyātil lil-mutawassimīn",
