        "latin_77": "inna fī żālika la`āyatal lil-mu`minīn",
        "latin_78": "wa ing kāna aṣ-ḥābul-aikati laẓālimīn",
        "latin_79": "fantaqamnā min-hum, wa innahumā labi`imāmim mubīn",
        "latin_80": "wa laqad każżaba aṣ-ḥābul-ḥijril-mursalīn",
        "latin_81": "wa ātaināhum āyātinā fa kānụ 'an-hā mu'riḍīn",
