        "latin_10": "huwallażī anzala minas-samā`i mā`al lakum min-hu syarābuw wa min-hu syajarun fīhi tusīmụn",
        "latin_11": "yumbitu lakum bihiz-zar'a waz-zaitụna wan-nakhīla wal-a'nāba wa ming kulliṡ-ṡamarāt, inna fī żālika la`āyatal liqaumiy yatafakkarụn",
        "latin_12": "wa sakhkhara lakumul-laila wan-nahāra wasy-syamsa wal-qamar, wan-nujụmu musakhkharātum bi`amrih, inna fī żālika la`āyātil liqaumiy ya'qilụn",
        "latin_13": "wa mā żara`a lakum fil-arḍi mukhtalifan alwānuh, inna fī żālika la`āyatal liqaumiy yażżakkarụn",
        "latin_14": "wa huwallażī sakhkharal-baḥra lita`kulụ min-hu laḥman ṭariyyaw wa tastakhrijụ min-hu ḥilyatan talbasụnahā, wa taral-fulka mawākhira fīhi wa litabtagụ min faḍlihī wa la'allakum tasykurụn",
        "latin_15": "wa alqā fil-arḍi rawāsiya an tamīda bikum wa an-hāraw wa subulal la'allakum tahtadụn",
