        "latin_17": "a fa may yakhluqu kamal lā yakhluq, a fa lā tażakkarụn",
        "latin_18": "wa in ta'uddụ ni'matallāhi lā tuḥṣụhā, innallāha lagafụrur raḥīm",
        "latin_19": "wallāhu ya'lamu mā tusirrụna wa mā tu'linụn",
        "latin_20": "wallażīna yad'ụna min dụnillāhi lā yakhluqụna syai`aw wa hum yukhlaqụn",
