        "latin_49": "qāla āmantum lahụ qabla an āżana lakum, innahụ lakabīrukumullażī 'allamakumus-siḥr, fa lasaufa ta'lamụn, la`uqaṭṭi'anna aidiyakum wa arjulakum min khilāfiw wa la`uṣallibannakum ajma'īn",
