        "latin_4": "allāhullażī khalaqas-samāwāti wal-arḍa wa mā bainahumā fī sittati ayyāmin ṡummastawā 'alal-'arsy, mā lakum min dụnihī miw waliyyiw wa lā syafī', a fa lā tatażakkarụn",
        "latin_5": "yudabbirul-amra minas-samā`i ilal-arḍi ṡumma ya'ruju ilaihi fī yauming kāna miqdāruhū alfa sanatim mimmā ta'uddụn",
        "latin_6": "żālika 'ālimul-gaibi wasy-syahādatil-'azīzur-raḥīm",
