        "latin_29": "mā yubaddalul-qaulu ladayya wa mā ana biẓallāmil lil-'abīd",
        "latin_30": "yauma naqụlu lijahannama halimtala`ti wa taqụlu hal mim mazīd",
        "latin_31": "wa uzlifatil-jannatu lil-muttaqīna gaira ba'īd",
        "latin_32": "hāżā mā tụ'adụna likulli awwābin ḥafīẓ",
        "latin_33": "man khasyiyar-raḥmāna bil-gaibi wa jā`a biqalbim munīb",
        "latin_34": "udkhulụhā bisalām, żālika yaumul-khulụd",
        "latin_35": "lahum mā yasyā`ụna fīhā wa ladainā mazīd",
        "latin_36": "wa kam ahlaknā qablahum ming qarnin hum asyaddu min-hum baṭsyan fa naqqabụ fil-bilād, hal mim maḥīṣ",
        "latin_37": "inna fī żālika lażikrā limang kāna lahụ qalbun au alqas-sam'a wa huwa syahīd",
        "latin_38": "wa laqad khalaqnas-samāwāti wal-arḍa wa mā bainahumā fī sittati ayyāmiw wa mā massanā mil lugụb",
        "latin_39": "faṣbir 'alā mā yaqụlụna wa sabbiḥ biḥamdi rabbika qabla ṭulụ'isy-syamsi wa qablal-gurụb",
        "latin_40": "wa minal-laili fa sabbiḥ-hu wa adbāras-sujụd",
        "latin_41": "wastami' yauma yunādil-munādi mim makāning qarīb",
        "latin_42": "yauma yasma'ụnaṣ-ṣaiḥata bil-ḥaqq, żālika yaumul-khurụj",
        "latin_43": "innā naḥnu nuḥyī wa numītu wa ilainal-maṣīr",
        "latin_44": "yauma tasyaqqaqul-arḍu 'an-hum sirā'ā, żālika ḥasyrun 'alainā yasīr",
        "latin_45": "naḥnu a'lamu bimā yaqụlụna wa mā anta 'alaihim bijabbār, fażakkir bil-qur`āni may yakhāfu wa'īd"
