        "latin_17": "i'lamū annallāha yuḥyil-arḍa ba'da mautihā, qad bayyannā lakumul-āyāti la'allakum ta'qilụn",
        "latin_18": "innal-muṣṣaddiqīna wal-muṣṣaddiqāti wa aqraḍullāha qarḍan ḥasanay yuḍā'afu lahum wa lahum ajrung karīm",
        "latin_19": "wallażīna āmanụ billāhi wa rusulihī ulā`ika humuṣ-ṣiddīqụna wasy-syuhadā`u 'inda rabbihim, lahum ajruhum wa nụruhum, wallażīna kafarụ wa każżabụ bi`āyātinā ulā`ika aṣ-ḥābul-jaḥīm",
        "latin_20": "i'lamū annamal-ḥayātud-dun-yā la'ibuw wa lahwuw wa zīnatuw wa tafākhurum bainakum wa takāṡurun fil-amwāli wal-aulād, kamaṡali gaiṡin a'jabal-kuffāra nabātuhụ ṡumma yahīju fa tarāhu muṣfarran ṡumma yakụnu huṭāmā, wa fil-ākhirati 'ażābun syadīduw wa magfiratum minallāhi wa riḍwān, wa mal-ḥayātud-dun-yā illā matā'ul-gurụr",
        "latin_21": "sābiqū ilā magfiratim mir rabbikum wa jannatin 'arḍuhā ka'arḍis-samā`i wal-arḍi u'iddat lillażīna āmanụ billāhi wa rusulih, żālika faḍlullāhi yu`tīhi may yasyā`, wallāhu żul-faḍlil-'aẓīm",
