        "latin_10": "a'addallāhu lahum 'ażāban syadīdan fattaqullāha yā ulil-albāb, allażīna āmanụ qad anzalallāhu ilaikum żikrā",
        "latin_11": "rasụlay yatlụ 'alaikum āyātillāhi mubayyinātil liyukhrijallażīna āmanụ wa 'amiluṣ-ṣāliḥāti minaẓ-ẓulumāti ilan-nụr, wa may yu`mim billāhi wa ya'mal ṣāliḥay yudkhil-hu jannātin tajrī min taḥtihal-an-hāru khālidīna fīhā abadā, qad aḥsanallāhu lahụ rizqā",
        "latin_12": "allāhullażī khalaqa sab'a samāwātiw wa minal-arḍi miṡlahunn, yatanazzalul-amru bainahunna lita'lamū annallāha 'alā kulli syai`ing qadīruw wa annallāha qad aḥāṭa bikulli syai`in 'ilmā"
